Main table constructor. Example use: 

   table []
     [ thead []
         [ tr []
             [ th [ ascending ] [ text "Material" ]
             , th [ numeric ] [ text "Quantity" ]
             , th [ numeric ] [ text "Unit Price" ]
             ]
         ]
     , tbody []
         [ tr []
             [ td [] [ text "Acrylic (Transparent)" ]
             , td [ numeric ] [ text "25" ]
             , td [ numeric ] [ text "$2.90" ]
             ]
         {- ... -}
         ]
     ]

